\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Joel m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba an iti, ez…® a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n gun m…®kemezir puvat…®, a gumazir manmagh…®n amizimra. Kantri Persia gavgavigha itir dughiam…®n a ti ike, kar dughiar Israelian gumazamiziba Babilon ategha ua Judan nguazim…®n izezim. 
\ip Dughiar bar kurar mam kantrin otoz…®, Joel an gari. Aruer ekiam isiragha biziba bar dagh amiz…®, da bar m…®s…®ngiz…®, odezir b…®zir ekiam uaghan otogha, dagheba ko bizibagh as…®ghas…®ghasava ami. Joel bizir kam…®n garima, a mati, gumazamizir God…®n apanim damuasava amiba, ikiangs…®zir akar mam me bagha izi. Me arazir kurabar amu mang…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Kotiar Ekiam…®n Dughiam otoght…®, a gumazamizir kurabagh as…®ghas…®gh, gumazamizir an ifongiam…®n g…®n zuiba derav…®ra me damuam. 
\ip Joel gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, me uan navibagh iraght…®, God men apangkuvigham. Akam inigha izir gumazim Joel…®n akabar aven, akar d…®k…®r…®zir ekiar mam iti, akar kam a Joel 2:28-32…®n iti. A ghaze, God uan Duam amadaght…®, a gumazamiziba bagh izam, gumazamizir aseba ko igiaba uaghara. God uan Duam Iesus…®n suren gumazamiziba bagha anemadazir dughiam…®n g…®n, Pita kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Bizir kam, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Joel…®n akam gamiz…®ma a guizbang…®ram oto. N…® Aposel 2:1-42…®n gan. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Odeziba Judan kantri gas…®ghas…®gha, ua gumazamiziba inigha God bagha izi 
